{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"生动的一课","authors":["时学东"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":9,"day":28}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"生动的一课"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时学东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放开歌喉唱赞歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起铁臂敲金锣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人阶级必须领导一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙儿喜气洋洋来庆贺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十多岁的张师傅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜得皱纹起漩窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起大旗迈健步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落牙的嘴呀笑呵呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“来！年青的同学们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大老粗给你们上一课……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张师傅打开衣襟敞前胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭抽的伤痕一尺多……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是压迫、剥削，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是苦难、饥饿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张师傅讲得文通理通有脉络，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么生动的一堂政治课！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说“剥削有功”？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是妄图再给我们套枷锁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“打倒中国赫鲁晓夫！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把他的画皮剥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大揭发、大控诉、大批判，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人心中烧燃仇恨的烈火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把资产阶级教育路线彻底埋葬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗批改的浪潮势如黄河……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}